folder: Stillwell Avenue & Neptune Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Stillwell Ave., east side, north from Neptune ave., showing the Coney Island Times building (No. 2753) and before it C. Kelly's auto blacksmith shop (No. 2761).

November 1924.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

folder: Neptune Avenue & Stillwell Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1) Neptune Ave., north side, east of Stillwell Ave., showing the N.Y. City Sewer Dept., tanks for this area.

October 1928.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) The same, further eastward from West 12th Street.

October 1928.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
